metadata.description: Hajime Sorayamaâ€™s Untitled_Shark Robot (Full) is an aquatic, metal shark slowly lurking through the dark ocean on a spinning, metallic card. Starting at the bottom of the ocean and slowly making its way to the surface, the Shark Robot eventually swims off the card and towards the viewer.
